Class PeriodCalculate

java.lang.Object
PeriodCalculate
public class PeriodCalculate extends Object
Functional class used to calculate and keep track of the period cycles; its functions include calculating the frequency, calculating the average length of period, predicting the ovulation dates, and tracking the progress of the current cycle.
